WEBVTT

00:08:58.542 --> 00:09:04.851
and think maybe their worries
are worth paying attention to.

00:09:04.875 --> 00:09:06.184
And finally,

00:09:06.208 --> 00:09:11.018
vaccines touch every single
life on the planet.

00:09:11.042 --> 00:09:13.434
What other health intervention,

00:09:13.458 --> 00:09:15.684
besides water,

00:09:15.708 --> 00:09:18.851
touches every single life?

00:09:18.875 --> 00:09:21.893
So if you're looking
for something to disrupt,

00:09:21.917 --> 00:09:23.667
it's a perfect stage.

00:09:24.708 --> 00:09:29.393
Perhaps that's one of the reasons
that we need to pay more attention

00:09:29.417 --> 00:09:32.976
and rebuild our trust in issues.